First Steps

    Skyrim Unbound Reborn: The list uses Skyrim Unbound for an alternate start. Configure your character and begin wherever you wish.

    Visual Customization:

        Use RaceMenu to adjust your character.

        OBody NG allows you to change the body of your character and NPCs in real-time.

    Followers:

        INIGO is available in Riften (jail).

        Nether's Follower Framework allows you to manage multiple followers.

    Game Overhauls:

        Mysticism expands magic with new spells.

        Summermyst adds unique enchantments.

        Valravn improves combat (blocking, stamina, etc.).

